#. Tag: title
#: referencemanual.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Reference"
msgstr "Käskude seletused"

#. Tag: title
#: referencemanual.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Ülevaade"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:6
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This chapter gives detailed explanations of all commands available in "
"&partman;. It is intended as a reference to accompany the information given "
"in <xref linkend=\"usermanual\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Järgnevalt selgitatakse üksikasjalikult kõiki partitsioonihalduri käske. See "
"on täiendus kasutajaliidese tutvustusele, mille andis <xref linkend="
"\"usermanual\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: referencemanual.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Menu"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Fail</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Välju</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Quits &partman;</action> without applying any pending operations. "
"The application will however ask you to confirm your choice to quit if there "
"are pending operations."
msgstr ""
"<action>Lõpetab partitsioonihalduri töö</action> ilma ühtegi ootel "
"operatsiooni teostamata. Rakendus küsib siiski sinu käest, kas soovid tõesti "
"väljuda, kui mõni operatsioon peaks ootel olema."

#. Tag: title
#: referencemanual.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Edit Menu"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Võta tagasi</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Undoes the last operation</action> that has been added to the "
"operation stack."
msgstr ""
"<action>Tühistab viimase operatsiooni</action>, mis on lisatud "
"operatsioonide nimekirja."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:46 referencemanual.docbook:62
#: referencemanual.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid "This command is only enabled if the list of operations is not empty."
msgstr ""
"Seda käsku saab kasutada ainult siis, kui operatsioonide nimekiri ei ole "
"tühi."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Clear</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Puhasta</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Clears the list of operations</action> without applying any of them."
msgstr ""
"<action>Puhastab operatsioonide nimekirja</action> ilma neist ühtegi "
"teostamata."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Apply</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Rakenda</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Applies the list of operations</action>. This command will apply all "
"operations in the list so that all changes are permanently written to your "
"disks. After the operations have been applied, the list is cleared and there "
"will be no way to undo any operation."
msgstr ""
"<action>Teostab operatsioonide nimekirja operatsioonid</action>. Selle "
"käsuga rakendatakse kõik nimekirjas olevad operatsioonid, millega "
"kirjutatakse kõik muudatused jäädavalt ketastele. Pärast operatsioonide "
"teostamist nimekiri puhastatakse ning pole enam mingit võimalust neid tagasi "
"võtta."

#. Tag: title
#: referencemanual.docbook:88
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "The <guimenu>Device</guimenu> Menu"
msgid "The Device Menu"
msgstr "Menüü <guimenu>Seade</guimenu>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:93
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Devices</guimenuitem>"
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Device</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Select Current Device</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Seadmed</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to select a device from a submenu with all available devices of "
"the system."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:105
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> "
#| "<guimenuitem>Refresh Devices</guimenuitem>"
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Device</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Refresh Devices</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Värskenda seadmeid</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Refreshes the devices</action>: This command forces &partman; to "
"scan and read the devices on your computer again. This may for example be "
"useful if you plugged in an external USB hard disk after you started "
"&partman;."
msgstr ""
"<action>Võimaldab värskendada seadmeid</action>: selle käsuga sunnitakse "
"partitsioonihaldur taas üle uurima kõik sinu arvuti seadmed. Sellest võib "
"olla kasu näiteks siis, kui oled pärast partitsioonihalduri käivitamist "
"ühendanud välise USB-kõvaketta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:119
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>N</keycap></"
#| "keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Device</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Create New "
#| "Partition Table</guimenuitem>"
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>N</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Device</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Partition "
"Table</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>N</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Seade</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Loo uus "
"partitsioonitabel</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:126
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<action>Creates a new partition table</action>: This command creates a "
#| "new and empty MSDOS partition table on the currently selected device. "
#| "This will delete all partitions on the device and all data on them, so "
#| "you will want to be careful with this command."
msgid ""
"<action>Creates a new partition table</action>: This command creates a new "
"and empty GPT or MSDOS partition table on the currently selected device. "
"This will delete all partitions on the device and all data on them, so you "
"will want to be careful with this command."
msgstr ""
"<action>Loob uue partitsioonitabeli</action>: selle käsuga luuakse parajasti "
"valitud seadmes uus ja tühi MSDOS partitsioonitabel. See kustutab kõik "
"seadme partitsioonid ja neil olevad andmed, nii et selle käsuga tasuks "
"ettevaatlik olla."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command is only enabled if a device is selected and no partition on "
"this device is currently mounted."
msgstr ""
"Seda käsku saab kasutada ainult siis, kui seade on valitud ja ükski seadme "
"partitsioon pole ühendatud."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:137
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Information</guimenuitem>"
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Device</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Export Partition Table</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Teave</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to export a list of all partitions on the selected device into a "
"file."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:149
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Information</guimenuitem>"
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Device</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Import Partition Table</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Teave</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allows you to import partition table from a previously exported file."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:156
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<action>Creates a new partition table</action>: This command creates a "
#| "new and empty MSDOS partition table on the currently selected device. "
#| "This will delete all partitions on the device and all data on them, so "
#| "you will want to be careful with this command."
msgid ""
"This will delete all partitions on the device and all data on them, so you "
"will want to be careful with this command."
msgstr ""
"<action>Loob uue partitsioonitabeli</action>: selle käsuga luuakse parajasti "
"valitud seadmes uus ja tühi MSDOS partitsioonitabel. See kustutab kõik "
"seadme partitsioonid ja neil olevad andmed, nii et selle käsuga tasuks "
"ettevaatlik olla."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:158
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This command is only enabled if a device is selected and no partition on "
#| "this device is currently mounted."
msgid ""
"This command is only enabled if a device is selected and no partition on "
"this device is currently mounted. Importing into logical devices such as LVM "
"Volume Groups is currently not supported."
msgstr ""
"Seda käsku saab kasutada ainult siis, kui seade on valitud ja ükski seadme "
"partitsioon pole ühendatud."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:164
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Log Output</guimenuitem>"
msgid "<guimenu>Device</guimenu> <guimenuitem>SMART Status</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Vaade</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Logi väljund</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows a SMART report. SMART is a monitoring system included in hard disk and "
"solid-state drives that detects and reports on various indicators of drive "
"reliability, with the intent of enabling the anticipation of hardware "
"failures."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:177
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<guimenu>Partition</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem>"
msgid "<guimenu>Device</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Partitsioon</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Omadused</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows information about currently selected devices. In this dialog you can "
"find capacity, sector sizes, partition table type as well as used and "
"maximum number of primary partitions."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: referencemanual.docbook:192
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "The <guimenu>Partition</guimenu> Menu"
msgid "The Partition Menu"
msgstr "Menüü <guimenu>Partitsioon</guimenu>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Partition</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Partitsioon</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uus</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Creates a new partition</action>: Opens the dialog to create a new "
"partition where you will be able to set type, size, position and file system "
"of the partition to create."
msgstr ""
"<action>Loob uue partitsiooni</action>: avatakse uue partitsiooni loomise "
"dialoog, kus saab määrata loodava partitsiooni tüübi, suuruse, asukoha ja "
"failisüsteemi."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please note that the partition table on a device may impose restrictions on "
"how many partitions can be created. MS-DOS partition tables, for example, "
"allow only four primary partitions."
msgstr ""
"Palun arvesta, et seadme partitsioonitabel võib piirata seda, kui palju "
"partitsioone saab luua. Näiteks MS-DOS partitsioonitabelid võimaldavad luua "
"ainult neli peamist partitsiooni."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command is only enabled if an unallocated area on a device is selected."
msgstr "Seda käsku saab kasutada ainult siis, kui valitud on seadme tühi ala."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Partition</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Resize/Move</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Partitsioon</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Muuda suurust/Liiguta</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:225
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<action>Resizes or moves a partition</action>: Opens the dialog to resize "
#| "or move an existing partition. Depending on the partition's file system "
#| "and the external tools installed on your computer, not all three possible "
#| "resize-related actions -- that is, moving the partition, making it "
#| "smaller (<quote>shrinking</quote> it) or making it larger "
#| "(<quote>growing</quote> it) -- may be available in this dialog. See <xref "
#| "linkend=\"menu-view-filesystemsupport\"/>."
msgid ""
"<action>Resizes or moves a partition</action>: Opens the dialog to resize or "
"move an existing partition. Depending on the partition's file system and the "
"external tools installed on your computer, not all three possible resize-"
"related actions -- that is, moving the partition, making it smaller "
"(<quote>shrinking</quote> it) or making it larger (<quote>growing</quote> "
"it) -- may be available in this dialog. See <xref linkend=\"menu-tools-"
"filesystemsupport\"/>."
msgstr ""
"<action>Muudab partitsiooni suurus või liigutab seda</action>: avatakse "
"dialoog, milles saab olemasoleva partitsiooni suurust muuta või seda "
"liigutada. Sõltuvalt partitsiooni failisüsteemis ja sinu arvutisse "
"paigaldatud välistest tööriistadest ei pruugi olla võimalik kasutada kõiki "
"kolme antud käsuga seotud võimalust, see tähendab partitsiooni liigutamist, "
"selle muutmist väiksemaks (<quote>kahandamist</quote>) või selle muutmist "
"suuremaks (<quote>kasvatamist</quote>). Vt. ka <xref linkend=\"menu-view-"
"filesystemsupport\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command is only enabled if a partition is selected that is not "
"currently mounted and whose file system can be shrunk, grown or moved. For "
"an extended partition, it is only enabled if none of the logicals in the "
"extended partition are mounted."
msgstr ""
"Seda käsku saab kasutada ainult siis, kui valitud partitsioon ei ole "
"ühendatud ning selle failisüsteemi saab kahandada, kasvatada või liigutada. "
"Laiendatud partitsiooni korral saab käsku kasutada ainult siis, kui ükski "
"partitsiooni loogilistest osadest ei ole ühendatud."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:235
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<shortcut><keycap>Del</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Partition</guimenu> "
#| "<guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem>"
msgid ""
"<shortcut>&Del;</shortcut> <guimenu>Partition</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Delete</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>Del</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Partitsioon</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Kustuta</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Deletes a partition</action>: This command deletes the currently "
"selected partition."
msgstr "<action>Kustutab partitsiooni</action>, mis on parajasti valitud."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:245 referencemanual.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command is only enabled if a partition is selected that is not "
"currently mounted. For an extended partition, it is only enabled if it does "
"not contain any logical partitions."
msgstr ""
"Seda käsku saab kasutada ainult siis, kui valitud partitsioon ei ole "
"ühendatud. Laiendatud partitsiooni korral saab käsku kasutada ainult siis, "
"kui see ei sisalda ühtegi loogilist partitsiooni."

